title: Smart Design Templates Vol 3
description:
Can be used as either a plug in for Smart Designer or use as stand alone.

Overview:

Smart Templates, Volume 3 artwork was designed to emulate popular \"retail\" styles from fashion and design leaders with 588 Smart Templates and over 800 clip art images. Innovative new tools are provided including \"distressed look\" overlays, mascots with interchangeable heads and customizable vector patterns. Smart Templates Volume 3 includes 12 themed categories including Mascots, Collegiate, Classic Sports, Action Sports, Patches, Stripes, Tribal/Flames, Tropical, Extreme, Patriotic and Events.
